query:
UPDATE handle_scorings SET (id, 
handle_id, 
status, 
created_at, 
me_json, 
tweets_json, 
mentions_json, 
post_count, 
impression_count, 
ghost_account, 
inflated_audience, 
followed, 
liked, 
replied, 
reposted, 
mentioned, 
online_engagement_score, 
online_engagement_override, 
online_engagement_override_reason, 
offline_engagement_score, 
offline_engagement_description, 
poll_id, 
poll_ends_at, 
poll_votes_updated_at, 
poll_none_votes, 
poll_average_votes, 
poll_high_votes, 
poll_reverse_votes, 
poll_score, 
poll_override, 
poll_override_reason, 
operational_status_score, 
operational_status_override, 
operational_status_override_reason, 
referrer_score, 
referrer_score_override, 
referrer_score_override_reason, 
holder_score, 
holder_score_override, 
holder_score_override_reason, 
audience_size, 
audience_size_override, 
audience_size_override_reason) = ((CASE $2::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $3 ELSE id END), (CASE $4::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $5 ELSE handle_id END), (CASE $6::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $7 ELSE status END), (CASE $8::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $9 ELSE created_at END), (CASE $10::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $11 ELSE me_json END), (CASE $12::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $13 ELSE tweets_json END), (CASE $14::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $15 ELSE mentions_json END), (CASE $16::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $17 ELSE post_count END), (CASE $18::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $19 ELSE impression_count END), (CASE $20::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $21 ELSE ghost_account END), (CASE $22::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $23 ELSE inflated_audience END), (CASE $24::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $25 ELSE followed END), (CASE $26::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $27 ELSE liked END), (CASE $28::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $29 ELSE replied END), (CASE $30::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $31 ELSE reposted END), (CASE $32::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $33 ELSE mentioned END), (CASE $34::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $35 ELSE online_engagement_score END), (CASE $36::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $37 ELSE online_engagement_override END), (CASE $38::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $39 ELSE online_engagement_override_reason END), (CASE $40::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $41 ELSE offline_engagement_score END), (CASE $42::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $43 ELSE offline_engagement_description END), (CASE $44::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $45 ELSE poll_id END), (CASE $46::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $47 ELSE poll_ends_at END), (CASE $48::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $49 ELSE poll_votes_updated_at END), (CASE $50::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $51 ELSE poll_none_votes END), (CASE $52::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $53 ELSE poll_average_votes END), (CASE $54::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $55 ELSE poll_high_votes END), (CASE $56::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $57 ELSE poll_reverse_votes END), (CASE $58::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $59 ELSE poll_score END), (CASE $60::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $61 ELSE poll_override END), (CASE $62::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $63 ELSE poll_override_reason END), (CASE $64::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $65 ELSE operational_status_score END), (CASE $66::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $67 ELSE operational_status_override END), (CASE $68::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $69 ELSE operational_status_override_reason END), (CASE $70::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $71 ELSE referrer_score END), (CASE $72::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $73 ELSE referrer_score_override END), (CASE $74::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $75 ELSE referrer_score_override_reason END), (CASE $76::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $77 ELSE holder_score END), (CASE $78::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $79 ELSE holder_score_override END), (CASE $80::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $81 ELSE holder_score_override_reason END), (CASE $82::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $83 ELSE audience_size END), (CASE $84::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $85 ELSE audience_size_override END), (CASE $86::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $87 ELSE audience_size_override_reason END)) WHERE id = $1 RETURNING id as "id!: i32", 
handle_id as "handle_id!: i32", 
status as "status!: HandleScoringStatus", 
created_at as "created_at!: DateTime < Utc >", 
me_json as "me_json!: Option < String >", 
tweets_json as "tweets_json!: Option < String >", 
mentions_json as "mentions_json!: Option < String >", 
post_count as "post_count!: i32", 
impression_count as "impression_count!: i32", 
ghost_account as "ghost_account!: bool", 
inflated_audience as "inflated_audience!: bool", 
followed as "followed!: bool", 
liked as "liked!: bool", 
replied as "replied!: bool", 
reposted as "reposted!: bool", 
mentioned as "mentioned!: bool", 
online_engagement_score as "online_engagement_score!: EngagementScore", 
online_engagement_override as "online_engagement_override!: Option < EngagementScore >", 
online_engagement_override_reason as "online_engagement_override_reason!: Option < String >", 
offline_engagement_score as "offline_engagement_score!: EngagementScore", 
offline_engagement_description as "offline_engagement_description!: Option < String >", 
poll_id as "poll_id!: Option < String >", 
poll_ends_at as "poll_ends_at!: Option < DateTime < Utc > >", 
poll_votes_updated_at as "poll_votes_updated_at!: Option < DateTime < Utc > >", 
poll_none_votes as "poll_none_votes!: i32", 
poll_average_votes as "poll_average_votes!: i32", 
poll_high_votes as "poll_high_votes!: i32", 
poll_reverse_votes as "poll_reverse_votes!: i32", 
poll_score as "poll_score!: Option < PollScore >", 
poll_override as "poll_override!: Option < PollScore >", 
poll_override_reason as "poll_override_reason!: Option < String >", 
operational_status_score as "operational_status_score!: OperationalStatus", 
operational_status_override as "operational_status_override!: Option < OperationalStatus >", 
operational_status_override_reason as "operational_status_override_reason!: Option < String >", 
referrer_score as "referrer_score!: bool", 
referrer_score_override as "referrer_score_override!: bool", 
referrer_score_override_reason as "referrer_score_override_reason!: Option < String >", 
holder_score as "holder_score!: bool", 
holder_score_override as "holder_score_override!: bool", 
holder_score_override_reason as "holder_score_override_reason!: Option < String >", 
audience_size as "audience_size!: i32", 
audience_size_override as "audience_size_override!: Option < i32 >", 
audience_size_override_reason as "audience_size_override_reason!: Option < String >"
